7:
I hope we'll have a good one
together, Stella. Alk.
16:
Oh, my darling Stella! You're
positively stunning as well!
21:
I can't believe you look good in
anything you wear...
24:
The complete and utter lack of
shame is another matter entirely...
28:
Oh? I don't recall giving either of you
permission to look or share your
opinions.
35:
Belsidia, Wicked Witch of the Rift. A
legendary figure who has worked in
the shadows since long before our
worlds merged.
37:
I've heard that she is a sworn enemy
of the Stratos line. What will you do
with that information, I wonder?
41:
Nothing? That doesn't sound like
someone I'd be capable of handling
in the first place.
48:
Last of the Stratos family. I've been
looking forward to our meeting.
51:
You've been naughty with my
Alky-Walky!
61:
I know what you did over the
summer! Having your way with him
however you liked...
69:
Life is so unfair! You beat me to all
the fun!
77:
I've already reflected on my
mistakes from then... Or rather, I've
done my best to forget all of it...
86:
What's there to forgive? I'm only
insulted you want to forget. You
should have a little more fun,
honestly.
95:
Isn't it simply delightful to yield to
one another and yearn for one
another?
98:
But the most tantalizing of all is the
change you derive from the
experience. And once you discover
the possibility of it...
106:
There's no going back, so why not
embrace change? Whatever your
desires, I fully support your pursuit of
them.
111:
I don't believe this is the sort of
behavior to be encouraged...
115:
Not in the habit of being honest with
ourselves, are we?
118:
You know what, why don't you come
with me?
133: What? No, it's gotta be this!
136: Let's see what the dice say...
140:
They're in favor of the little lady
today! She wins!
143:
N-no way, that's like the fifth time in
a row. That ain't possible!
145:
It is as long as you believe in the
flames.
148:
Let me see those dice! This has
gotta be rigged!
150:
We can always use dice of your
choice if you believe there to be foul
play.
153: Then let's go! I've got you now!
158:
We've overstayed our welcome,
Lilith. Time to go!
167: Ahahaha! What a thrill that was!
170:
Are you sure you're fine with the end
result? We could've milked them for
all they're worth if we'd played our
hand right.
174: I didn't participate to win money.
176:
I simply wanted to... have a little bit
of mischievous fun. That was the
goal, wasn't it?
180:
Hahaha, it was, but don't tell Light.
He'll never let me hear the end of it.
185:
Can I ask you something? Why were
you so interested in me in the first
place?
188:
The Stratos family as it is now poses
no threat to you.
193:
Oh, the thought never crossed my
mind. How do I put it...
204:
For one, both you and I can't hold
ourselves back, even when it comes
to mischief.
207:
But more than that... You were able
accomplish what I never could.
209: You're just like Alk in that regard.
213:
...You truly think so? I feel as if I'm
always one step behind him.
216:
Hehehe, he sounds like he makes a
worthy rival.
218:
Why not pluck up your courage and
spice things up a bit?
223:
I am perfectly fine on that front,
thank you!
227: A shame. Well, shall we head back?
230: Take me hand, and don't let go.
